name: GoGo for the Gold
overview: 12 Gogo boys from across the country descend on Hollywood to compete for 10 Thousand dollars and the title of 'America's #1 Champion Gogo Superstar... Star.' The contestants are judged by a panel of Gogo experts and compete in challenges to find out who stays and who go-goes home.

episodes.name: Lookin' for a S.T.U.D: Super Talented Underwear Dancer
Teeny Tiny Box
episodes.overview: The Gogos compete in the “Tiny Box Challenge” and must keep it sexy and looking good while dancing on a teeny tiny box.

episodes.name: Twerking for Grandma
episodes.overview: The Gogos get a “Twerking Tutorial”from Jojo Guadz and then must use their new skills while performing for a group of senior citizens in the pursuit to become “‘America’s #1 Champion Gogo Superstar... Star.’

episodes.name: No Pants-er Romancers
episodes.overview: The Gogos get a surprise performance from Burlesque Hall Of Famer and guest judge, Jett Adore and then must create and perform their own burlesque performances as duos.

episodes.name: Multi Media Superstar Stars
episodes.overview: The countdown to the crown is on as the Top 4 gogos compete in the 5 tiered Multi Media challenge where they must participate in photo shoots, interviews and create viral videos to prove they can be “‘America’s #1 Champion Gogo Superstar... Star.

episodes.name: Back & Baring It Al
episodes.overview: With the grand finale one week away, all 12 Gogos return to talk about the highlights and low lights of the season and the Top 4 clear the air about their behind the scenes drama.

episodes.name: Grand Finale
episodes.overview: The Top 4 compete in a runway challenge featuring all the previous contestants but only the final 2 will face off in “The Stripdown” tofind out who will become ‘America’s #1 Champion Gogo Superstar... Star.’

episodes.name: A Whole New Package
episodes.overview: A new crop of 12 Gogo boys from across the country descend on Hollywood to compete for the title of ‘America’s #1 Champion Gogo Superstar... Star.’ Hosted by Jonny McGovern.

episodes.name: Stripper Pole Control
episodes.overview: The Gogos compete to show off their stripper pole skills for the Gogo Gods and guest judge Johnny Scruff. Hosted by Jonny McGovern.

episodes.name: Center Of Attention
episodes.overview: The Gogos face off in head to head gogo battles with a twist... they must perform on teeny tiny gogo boxes! Hosted by Jonny McGovern.

episodes.name: Heel Appeal
episodes.overview: The Gogos must perform a high heel gogo routine for a tipping audience of famous drag queens. Hosted by Jonny McGovern.

episodes.name: Lap Dance Champ
episodes.overview: The Gogos compete in a challenge to be the “Lap Dance Champ” where they must give lap dances to mystery VIP clients. Hosted by Jonny McGovern.

episodes.name: Music Video Vix-Hims
episodes.overview: The Gogos must write and record verses for a new GG4TG track and then compete to give the hottest performance in the music video. Hosted by Jonny McGovern.
